title: UT2004 - Extract and Play (Online Play)
description:
This is Unreal Tournament 2004, patched to v3369.

Online play = OK!

Comes with Community Bonus Pack 1 and 2, as well as some custom skins and models. Since Skincity's download links are all down, you can get more at ut.rushbase.net/beyondunreal/skincity/ut2k4


==INSTRUCTIONS==

1- If you don't have 7zip installed, download and install it
2- Right click and Extract UT2004.7z
3- Navigate to UT2004/System and run UT2004.exe
4- Have fun!
